
  Shuppet    Ghost Type Pokémon

  SHUPPET is attracted by feelings 
  of jealousy and vindictiveness. 
   If someone develops strong feelings 
  of vengeance, Shuppet will 
  appear in a swarm and line up 
  beneath the eaves of that person’s 
  home. 
